'''Yazidis in Russia''' may refer to people born in or residing in the [[Russia]] of full or partial [[Yazidis|Yazidi]] origin.
There are about 60,586<ref name=Russiancensus>{{cite web|title=Всероссийская перепись населения 2010 г. Национальный состав населения Российской Федерации|url=http://demoscope.ru/weekly/ssp/rus_nac_10.php|work=Demoscope|publisher=Demoscope.ru|accessdate=26 October 2013}}</ref> [[Yazidis]] living in [[Russia]], primarily in [[Moscow]] (10,000) and in other agglomerations.
